skins.shipDescription: Kagerou-class destroyer number fourteen C Tanikaze.
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm Tanikaze, Kagerou-class destroyer number fourteen. I served as the flagship of Destroyer Division 17. There were a lot of aircraft in the Battle of Midway, but I hardly got bombed at all. Hamakaze-chan and I sunk a certain ship in the Kula Gulf... Hehehe~
skins.acquisition: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Commander, will you take me home?
skins.login: I'm right here if you need me.
skins.details: Midway? I believe we won that battle... O-or am I wrong again?!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Hamakaze-chan, you need to ease up a little! Pokey-poke~
skins.secretaryIdle2: Y-Yukikaze's coming here? W-we should be able to get along... Hopefully...
skins.secretaryIdle3: I always feel at ease when you're here with me, Commander.
skins.secretaryTouch: Wah! I wish you'd stop poking my cheek like that... Mmph...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Please, don't poke anything but my cheek!

skins.shipDescription: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Oh wow, a b-butterfly?! It really is a butterfly! Is this for me? Thank you, Commander!
skins.acquisition: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Oh wow, a b-butterfly?! It really is a butterfly! Is this for me? Thank you, Commander!
skins.secretaryIdle1: I really wonder... What might Urakaze-chan and Isokaze-chan be doing right now...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Something good is going to happen today, Commander.
skins.secretaryIdle3: You're a very warmhearted person, Commander.
skins.secretaryTouch: Wah! This time I'll poke you in return! Poke! Poke poke~!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Ah, I see! It's my turn now! Poke poke... Scratch scratch... Can I nap while you give me a piggyback, Commander? ...Zzzzz....

skins.shipDescription: The butterfly flew... Huh? Where did it...? Hamakaze? Hamakaze?! Huh? Where are Urakaze and Isokaze? Where did...? We said we'd all go to the beach, so where did they go...?
skins.acquisition: The butterfly flew... Huh? Where did it...? Hamakaze? Hamakaze?! Huh? Where are Urakaze and Isokaze? Where did...? We said we'd all go to the beach, so where did they go...?
skins.login: Commander, do you know where my sisters are? We promised we'd go to the beach, together...
skins.details: Would you like to go to the beach with us, Commander? I want to build sandcastles with everyone!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Ugh... I want to invite Yukikaze, but... she's hard to approach...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander, are my life jacket and float ring in order?
skins.secretaryIdle3: We're going to the beach... so Isokaze shouldn't ask me to play warring states with her, hopefully...
